llo 雪雪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5fq87t1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5fq87t1.jpg&h=979ca43b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n資深傳媒人潘小濤早前向商台辭職，離開工作了15年的地方。小濤今日最後一天主持《在晴朗的一天出發》，盧覓雪（Michell）在節目尾聲時突然現身直播室，原來她將接替小濤，由下星期一開始再次回歸《晴朗》的團隊主持節目。林海峰說︰「我們真的等了很久喇﹗Michell﹗Michell終於回來和我們一齊主持《晴朗》﹗」盧覓雪表示他也等了12年，林海峰說︰「點止我一個等你12年﹗聽眾也等了你好耐﹗」盧覓雪笑言她肯回來，是因為見商台的防護措施做得不錯﹗林海峰笑問新城是否有叫過她開咪？小濤最後說︰「黑暗的盡頭就是光明，各位再見﹗」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200807/1596778970807/%E7%9D%BD%E9%81%9512%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E3%80%8A%E6%99%B4%E6%9C%97%E3%80%8B-%E7%9B%A7%E8%A6%93%E9%9B%AA%E6%8E%A5%E6%BD%98%E5%B0%8F%E6%BF%A4%E6%A3%92%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6%8C%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200807%2F1596778970807%2F%25E7%259D%25BD%25E9%2581%259512%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2599%25B4%25E6%259C%2597%25E3%2580%258B-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E8%25A6%2593%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25BD%2598%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25BF%25A4%25E6%25A3%2592%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDKf05AUSLZuDOcHdeYvmXak%3D&h=3ec3e3b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200807%2F1596778970807%2F%25E7%259D%25BD%25E9%2581%259512%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25AD%25B8%25E3%2580%258A%25E6%2599%25B4%25E6%259C%2597%25E3%2580%258B-%25E7%259B%25A7%25E8%25A6%2593%25E9%259B%25AA%25E6%258E%25A5%25E6%25BD%2598%25E5%25B0%258F%25E6%25BF%25A4%25E6%25A3%2592%25E5%2581%259A%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258C%2581&h=146c4b48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200807/1596778970807/%E7%9D%BD%E9%81%9512%E5%B9%B4%E5%9B%9E%E6%AD%B8%E3%80%8A%E6%99%B4%E6%9C%97%E3%80%8B-%E7%9B%A7%E8%A6%93%E9%9B%AA%E6%8E%A5%E6%BD%98%E5%B0%8F%E6%BF%A4%E6%A3%92%E5%81%9A%E4%B8%BB%E6